    %% Ingress → Internal flows
    Router -->|"HTTP/80 or HTTPS/443<br/>plaintext/TLS<br/>None"| Predictor
    EnvoyGW -->|"TLS (EnvoyFilter)<br/>mTLS"| AuthorinoSvc

