    K8sAPI -->|"Webhook calls<br/>TLS client auth"| WebhookSvc
    WebhookSvc -->|"HTTPS/9443<br/>TLS"| Manager

    %% Discovery Server
    DiscoveryServer -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount"| K8sAPI

    %% Egress flows
    Manager -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>API Key (Bearer)"| NGCAPI
    Manager -->|"HTTP/HTTPS<br/>configurable<br/>Bearer Token"| ModelReg

